{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-note-js","path":"/extjs-grid-cell-tooltip-and-messagebox/","result":{"data":{"remark":{"fields":{"path":"extjs-grid-cell-tooltip-and-messagebox"},"meta":{"title":""},"headings":[{"value":"ExtJs grid cell tooltip and messagebox"}],"html":"<h1>ExtJs grid cell tooltip and messagebox</h1>\n<p>Here is code, for displaying tooltip or message box.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">cust</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">val<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> meta<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> record</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> hdn1 <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> record<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>data<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>hdn1\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> hdn2 <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> record<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>data<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>hdn2\n\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> icon <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> val <span class=\"token operator\">></span> <span class=\"token number\">5</span> <span class=\"token operator\">?</span> <span class=\"token string\">'http://rabota.ua/Theme/img/chek_icon.gif'</span> <span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'http://rabota.ua/Theme/img/cancel_icon.gif'</span>\n\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> tip <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"&lt;img src='\"</span> <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> icon <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"' />&lt;br />\"</span>\n  tip <span class=\"token operator\">+=</span> <span class=\"token string\">'hdn1: '</span> <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> hdn1 <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> <span class=\"token string\">'&lt;br />'</span>\n  tip <span class=\"token operator\">+=</span> <span class=\"token string\">'hdn2: '</span> <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> hdn2 <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> <span class=\"token string\">'&lt;br />'</span>\n  tip <span class=\"token operator\">+=</span> <span class=\"token string\">'&lt;br />'</span>\n  tip <span class=\"token operator\">+=</span> <span class=\"token string\">'&lt;b>SUM:&lt;/b> '</span> <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> val <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> <span class=\"token string\">'&lt;br />'</span>\n\n  meta<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>attr <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">'ext:qtip=\"'</span> <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> tip <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> <span class=\"token string\">'\" ext:qtitle=\"Tip FOR CUSTOM FIELD\"'</span>\n\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> mt <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">''</span>\n  mt <span class=\"token operator\">+=</span> <span class=\"token string\">'&amp;lt;b&amp;gt;Cusomt info&amp;lt;/b&amp;gt;&amp;lt;br /&amp;gt;'</span>\n  mt <span class=\"token operator\">+=</span> <span class=\"token string\">'&amp;lt;img src=&amp;quot;'</span> <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> icon <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> <span class=\"token string\">'&amp;quot; /&amp;gt;&amp;lt;br /&amp;gt;'</span>\n  mt <span class=\"token operator\">+=</span> <span class=\"token string\">'&amp;lt;i&amp;gt;hdn1:&amp;lt;/i&amp;gt; '</span> <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> hdn1 <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> <span class=\"token string\">'&amp;lt;br /&amp;gt;'</span>\n  mt <span class=\"token operator\">+=</span> <span class=\"token string\">'&amp;lt;i&amp;gt;hdn2:&amp;lt;/i&amp;gt; '</span> <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> hdn2 <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> <span class=\"token string\">'&amp;lt;br /&amp;gt;'</span>\n  mt <span class=\"token operator\">+=</span> <span class=\"token string\">'&amp;lt;br /&amp;gt;'</span>\n  mt <span class=\"token operator\">+=</span> <span class=\"token string\">'&amp;lt;b style=&amp;quot;color:red&amp;quot;&amp;gt;SUM:&amp;lt;/b&amp;gt; '</span> <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> val\n\n  mt <span class=\"token operator\">+=</span>\n    <span class=\"token string\">'&amp;lt;br /&amp;gt;&amp;lt;br /&amp;gt;&amp;lt;small&amp;gt;via &amp;lt;a href=&amp;quot;http://rabota.ua&amp;quot; target=&amp;quot;_blank&amp;quot;&amp;gt;rabota.ua&amp;lt;/a&amp;gt; and yes, mac was here :)&amp;lt;/small&amp;gt;'</span>\n\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> ret <span class=\"token operator\">=</span>\n    <span class=\"token string\">'&lt;a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"Ext.MessageBox.alert(\\'Info for custom field\\', \\''</span> <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> mt <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> <span class=\"token string\">'\\');return false;\">'</span> <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> val <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> <span class=\"token string\">'&lt;/a>'</span>\n  <span class=\"token comment\">//console.log(record);</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> ret\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>It is renderer used for field that contain sum of two other fields.</p>\n<p>Data for this field must be prepared on server, in other case you will not be able to sort\\filter field.</p>"}},"pageContext":{"id":"e9d7f864-7622-5dad-a049-70a1b4328cec"}},"staticQueryHashes":[],"slicesMap":{}}